 \lim\sup\left|\frac{a_{n+1}}{a_n}\right| \ \ \ \ \ \mbox{and} \ \ \ \ \ \lim_{n\to\infty}\left|\frac{a_{n+1}}{a_n}\right| 
 b_n = \left|\frac{a_{n+1}}{a_n}\right| 
n = 1, 2, \dots 
(a_n \neq 0)
\lim\sup_{n\rightarrow \infty} b_n = \inf_{ n \rightarrow \infty} \left(\sup_{k \geq n} b_k\right).
\lim_{n \rightarrow \infty} b_n
